## ğŸ§® Sample DAX Measures
```DAX
Total Runs = SUM(Matches[Total_Runs])

Total Matches = DISTINCTCOUNT(Matches[Match_ID])

Win Percentage = DIVIDE(
    COUNTROWS(FILTER(Matches, Matches[Winning_Team] = Matches[Team])),
    [Total Matches]
)

Average Score = AVERAGE(Matches[Team_Score])

Top Run Scorer = CALCULATE(
    SUM(Players[Runs]),
    FILTER(Players, Players[Runs] = MAX(Players[Runs]))
)
